horsentp.stp

Interface Data


  • public interface Data
    This interface defines the behavior for a data objects.

    The responsibilities of this interface is

    1. Tell the API how what properties it has.
    2. Read/Write the values of those properties.

    readProperty and writeProperty should be opposites of each other for the API to work correctly.
